Hello? Hello?

24:27.567 --> 24:28.868
Can anyone help me?

24:28.901 --> 24:31.604
I seem to be stuck
in this woman's brain.

24:31.638 --> 24:34.974
Wow, she spends a lot of time
thinking about fountains.
